"{\"uid\": \"abc.net.au-news-2024-08-11-paris-olympics-raygun-anna-meares-defends-breaker-104210672\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Personalise the news and  stay in the know  Emergency  Backstory  Newsletters  \\u4e2d\\u6587\\u65b0\\u95fb  BERITA BAHASA INDONESIA  TOK PISIN  Find any issues using dark mode?Please let us know  Sport  Topic:Olympic Games  Australia's Raygun faced a wave of online derision for her performance at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BAHASA INDONESIA\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.7335026103844354, \"rank\": 0.3633152836083331, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1404044703138317e-25, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Elsa)  Australia's Olympic chief has slammed critics of breakdancer Rachael Gunn as typical of misogynistic abuse that female athletes have historically had to endure.\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_Einstein\", \"score\": 0.5367076500248522, \"rank\": 0.506058026031755, \"text\": \"Elsa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_Einstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_Einstein\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.7335026103844354, \"rank\": 0.3633152836083331, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999978831511, \"rank\": 1.902710187083402e-09, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 385, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9920281073197157, \"rank\": 0.008031163113602906, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chef de mission Anna Meares said Gunn should be applauded for her courage, rather than pilloried for her performance at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}, {\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9920281073197157, \"rank\": 0.008031163113602906, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, known as Raygun, failed to score a point when breaking made its debut as an Olympic sport in Paris on Friday.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 631, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1404044703138317e-25, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995175131, \"rank\": 4.827002702106618e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn has since been a target of criticism for not only her performance but her appearance, online and in some mainstream media.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9920281073197157, \"rank\": 0.008031163113602906, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love Rachael,\\\" Meares told reporters.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 870, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999978831511, \"rank\": 1.902710187083402e-09, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rachael 'Raygun' Gunn is Australia's first and possibly only female breaker at the Olympics, with the event not on the schedule for the LA Games.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999978831511, \"rank\": 1.902710187083402e-09, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1404044703138317e-25, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9920281073197157, \"rank\": 0.008031163113602906, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.7335026103844354, \"rank\": 0.3633152836083331, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Cameron Spencer)  \\\"What has occurred on social media with trolls and keyboard warriors, and taking those comments and giving them air time, has been really disappointing.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Children_of_General_Hospital\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cameron Spencer\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Children_of_General_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Children_of_General_Hospital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Raygun is an absolutely loved member of this Olympic team.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has represented the Olympic team, the Olympic spirit, with great enthusiasm.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I absolutely love her courage.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love her character and I feel very disappointed for her, that she has come under the attack that she has.\\\"\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, a 36-year-old Australian university lecturer, lost all three of her round-robin battles by a combined score of 54-0.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9920281073197157, \"rank\": 0.008031163113602906, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9924902859395377, \"rank\": 0.007200435571358434, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 2008, she was locked in a room crying, being involved in a male-dominated sport as the only woman,\\\" Meares said.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's first breaker, Raygun, bows out of the Paris Olympics with a performance she described as \\\"different and creative\\\".\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.7335026103844354, \"rank\": 0.3633152836083331, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1404044703138317e-25, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it took great courage for her to continue on and fight for her opportunity to participate in a sport that she loved.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That got her to winning the Olympic qualifying event to be here in Paris.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995175131, \"rank\": 4.827002702106618e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is the best breakdancer female that we have for Australia.\\\"\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2149, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.7335026103844354, \"rank\": 0.3633152836083331, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meares likened the criticism to historic misogynistic abuse directed at female athletes as they fought for recognition in the sporting world.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now you look at the history of what we have had as women athletes, have faced in terms of criticism, belittlement, judgement, and simple comments like 'they should not be there',\\\" she said  \\\"One hundred years ago, leading into Paris 1924, Australia sent a team of 37 athletes - none were women.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2533, \"end\": 2543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7707465217270247, \"rank\": 0.2974434159747478, \"text\": \"Paris 1924\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.7335026103844354, \"rank\": 0.3633152836083331, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One hundred years later, we have 256 women representing here.\\\"\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, 16-year-old Australian Jeff 'J-Attack' Dunne was also unable to make it out of the round-robin stage in the men's event held on Saturday night.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2690, \"end\": 2700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9924902859395377, \"rank\": 0.007200435571358434, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dunne suffered three straight losses although at least collected a point in both his second and third battles.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese praised Raygun's performance in a statement.\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Prime Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2961, \"end\": 2977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}, {\"begin\": 2986, \"end\": 2992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1404044703138317e-25, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics is about people participating in sport.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a good thing and Raygun had a crack,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3102, \"end\": 3108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1404044703138317e-25, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Good on her and a big shout-out to her.\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is in the Australian tradition of people having a go.\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3189, \"end\": 3199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9924902859395377, \"rank\": 0.007200435571358434, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's had a go representing our country and that's a good thing.\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whether [athletes have] won gold medals or just done their best, that is all we ask for.\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the participating that is really important.\\\"\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Albanese expressed his \\\"hope\\\" that young people watching the 2024 Olympics would be encouraged to \\\"have a go\\\" at the Brisbane Olympics in 2032.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3443, \"end\": 3451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He called Australia's standing at the Paris Olympics a \\\"magnificent result\\\" and \\\"the best performance in any Olympics ever\\\".\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3598, \"end\": 3607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.7335026103844354, \"rank\": 0.3633152836083331, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AAP  Topic:Cricket  Topic:Cricket  Topic:Courts  Topic:NRL  Topic:NRL  Topic:Domestic Violence  Topic:Social Media  Topic:Federal Government  Topic:War  Topic:Royalty  Topic:Domestic Violence  Topic:Royalty  Topic:War  Australia  France  Olympic Games  Sport  Topic:Domestic Violence  Topic:Social Media  Topic:Federal Government  Topic:War  Topic:Royalty  Topic:Rural and Remote Communities  Topic:Pollution  Topic:Geography  Topic:Royalty  We acknowledge Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples as the First Australians and Traditional Custodians of the lands where we live, learn, and work.\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 4313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3769, \"end\": 3772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\", \"score\": 0.9972142386046233, \"rank\": 0.002754314711253623, \"text\": \"NRL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43